com.hazelcast.map.impl.querycache

Interface QueryCacheContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientQueryCacheContext, NodeQueryCacheContext

    public interface QueryCacheContext
    A global context which contains all sub-contexts which are responsible for all QueryCache life-cycle management phases.

    Any functionality for a QueryCache should be accessed on this context. It also helps to make abstractions over auxiliary services to provide different implementations on client and on node sides.
